            <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-siitec-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z"></path></svg>
                Marcas
